1
00:00:18,940 --> 00:00:23,880
♪Only after bloom comes fruit♪

2
00:00:25,290 --> 00:00:29,260
♪Who says glory must fade to the past♪

3
00:00:31,920 --> 00:00:37,010
♪Only through thunder
do you reach the clouds♪

4
00:00:38,210 --> 00:00:43,120
♪Who made you the crown of every peak♪

5
00:00:44,650 --> 00:00:47,930
♪I stand at the center of the stage♪

6
00:00:47,930 --> 00:00:51,000
♪My shadow is pinned against the wall♪

7
00:00:51,710 --> 00:00:56,660
♪Facing the light earns every medal♪

8
00:00:57,700 --> 00:01:00,880
♪Little birds,
save your needless pecking♪

9
00:01:00,880 --> 00:01:04,160
♪The open sky rises high♪

10
00:01:04,700 --> 00:01:09,830
♪When night falls,
the moon begins to shine♪

11
00:01:10,600 --> 00:01:13,860
♪I stand in the heart of these lands♪

12
00:01:13,860 --> 00:01:17,220
♪My shadow bears no crown or robe♪

13
00:01:17,630 --> 00:01:23,300
♪Then I know truth needs no disguise♪

14
00:01:23,710 --> 00:01:26,960
♪The green hills see me as I am♪

15
00:01:26,960 --> 00:01:30,290
♪Like dew, lightning,
and moon on the river♪

16
00:01:30,690 --> 00:01:34,730
♪Showing me exactly who I am♪

17
00:01:34,730 --> 00:01:35,980
=The Lead=

18
00:01:36,020 --> 00:01:37,900
=Episode 31=

19
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:01,600
Do you want some liangpi?

20
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:05,190
I caught you.

21
00:02:06,070 --> 00:02:08,280
I spent half a year growing this plant.

22
00:02:08,280 --> 00:02:09,350
It finally bloomed.

23
00:02:09,350 --> 00:02:10,710
I only got this bright one.

24
00:02:10,710 --> 00:02:11,710
Why did you snap it off?

25
00:02:20,600 --> 00:02:22,070
I just thought it looked nice.

26
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:23,360
Don't be mad.

27
00:02:24,320 --> 00:02:26,150
How about I buy it?

28
00:02:26,150 --> 00:02:27,320
I'll buy the whole pot.

29
00:02:27,750 --> 00:02:29,350
Did I grow it just to sell it to you?

30
00:02:29,470 --> 00:02:30,470
Of course not.

31
00:02:31,030 --> 00:02:32,560
Then how should we settle this?

32
00:02:32,670 --> 00:02:33,510
Ten yuan.

33
00:02:33,670 --> 00:02:34,960
Fine, ten yuan.

34
00:02:39,320 --> 00:02:40,250
Here.

35
00:02:43,920 --> 00:02:45,310
Such a beautiful flower.

36
00:02:45,310 --> 00:02:46,760
Wasn't it better off in the pot?

37
00:02:46,760 --> 00:02:48,040
Why put it in this ugly bottle?

38
00:02:48,040 --> 00:02:49,400
How long can it live?

39
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:50,280
Let's not be mad.

40
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:51,150
Don't be mad.

41
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:53,350
I'll make you some liangpi.

42
00:02:53,510 --> 00:02:54,920
With chili and vinegar, right?

43
00:02:54,920 --> 00:02:56,000
Coming right up.

44
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:56,840
Just wait a sec.

45
00:02:58,760 --> 00:02:59,610
To go.

46
00:02:59,640 --> 00:03:00,480
I'm busy at the shop.

47
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:01,960
Alright, alright.

48
00:03:02,870 --> 00:03:03,840
Don't be mad.

49
00:03:05,870 --> 00:03:06,730
It won't happen again.

50
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:08,430
- Here.
- Hand me the chopsticks.

51
00:03:10,790 --> 00:03:11,630
Grab two pairs.

52
00:03:11,630 --> 00:03:13,620
(Stir-fried liangfen)

53
00:03:20,640 --> 00:03:21,480
Next time,

54
00:03:22,350 --> 00:03:23,310
can we not do this?

55
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:25,480
I'll be more careful next time.

56
00:03:25,950 --> 00:03:27,000
So childish.

57
00:03:29,480 --> 00:03:30,320
Sanyuan.

58
00:03:31,636 --> 00:03:32,769
How many bowls have you had?

59
00:03:33,480 --> 00:03:34,680
Ma'am, get me a bowl.

60
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:36,200
Extra chili and vinegar.

61
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:37,200
I know.

62
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:42,880
Ma'am,

63
00:03:44,590 --> 00:03:45,750
you like growing flowers too?

64
00:03:47,710 --> 00:03:49,840
This is not good enough.

65
00:03:49,910 --> 00:03:51,240
They barely bloom at all.

66
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:52,960
If you like flowers, say so.

67
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:54,430
I'll get you a nice pot later.

68
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:56,240
That's a money tree, not a flower.

69
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:57,080
You got one?

70
00:03:57,710 --> 00:03:59,800
Is it making money or losing it?

71
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:01,080
Don't you know?

72
00:04:06,030 --> 00:04:08,030
Come with me after you eat.

73
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:10,680
Relax, I'll set it all up.

74
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:13,080
Come on, don't just eat. Drink.

75
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:14,240
Drink up, drink up.

76
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:15,080
Mr. Liu.

77
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:17,190
- Come on.
- Hongbing.

78
00:04:17,190 --> 00:04:18,400
Sit, sit. Have a seat.

79
00:04:18,400 --> 00:04:19,360
You're too late.

80
00:04:19,590 --> 00:04:20,430
We've been waiting.

81
00:04:20,710 --> 00:04:21,840
How many rounds has it been?

82
00:04:21,840 --> 00:04:22,893
Look how red your face is.

83
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:27,120
Hongbing.

84
00:04:27,470 --> 00:04:28,400
Later, I'll take you

85
00:04:28,400 --> 00:04:29,310
to a really great spot.

86
00:04:29,870 --> 00:04:30,710
I'm not going.

87
00:04:31,470 --> 00:04:32,310
What's with you?

88
00:04:32,910 --> 00:04:34,960
You weren't like this in Chang'an.

89
00:04:35,190 --> 00:04:36,120
What's going on?

90
00:04:36,150 --> 00:04:37,120
Have you become a monk?

91
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:38,360
Not into fun anymore?

92
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:39,680
Come on, Hongbing. What's up?

93
00:04:40,030 --> 00:04:40,960
Listen.

94
00:04:41,030 --> 00:04:42,560
We need to talk business today.

95
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:43,400
Got it?

96
00:04:43,750 --> 00:04:47,470
Who can reach the leader
over the provincial troupe?

97
00:04:48,960 --> 00:04:49,840
The provincial troupe?

98
00:04:49,960 --> 00:04:50,910
What are you doing?

99
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:52,470
Why?

100
00:04:52,750 --> 00:04:54,150
Don't worry about it.

101
00:04:54,960 --> 00:04:56,150
This is serious business.

102
00:04:56,910 --> 00:04:58,470
The higher the leader, the better.

103
00:04:59,030 --> 00:05:00,000
Have a drink first.

104
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:03,200
There's hope.

105
00:05:04,030 --> 00:05:05,030
Drink up, drink up.

106
00:05:06,840 --> 00:05:08,120
Open your eyes and listen to me.

107
00:05:09,630 --> 00:05:11,190
Ningzhou County Cultural Center

108
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:14,190
used to rely on art and literature

109
00:05:14,280 --> 00:05:16,400
to make a name
in the province and region.

110
00:05:17,150 --> 00:05:20,470
Later, I managed to push art and novels

111
00:05:20,870 --> 00:05:22,870
right out of the cultural center.

112
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:24,470
What did I rely on?

113
00:05:24,870 --> 00:05:26,190
My brain.

114
00:05:26,190 --> 00:05:28,030
- Use your brain!
- I'm starving.

115
00:05:28,030 --> 00:05:29,120
Can we just eat first?

116
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:30,750
Who exactly are we waiting for?

117
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:32,190
You have to wait.

118
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:34,750
Who can track down this leader for me?

119
00:05:35,870 --> 00:05:37,470
See that car parked outside?

120
00:05:38,080 --> 00:05:39,240
A month for free.

121
00:05:42,570 --> 00:05:43,430
Director Ding.

122
00:05:43,430 --> 00:05:44,680
Isn't it about business?

123
00:05:44,680 --> 00:05:45,593
Why are we here?

124
00:05:45,604 --> 00:05:46,995
What do you expect in a restaurant?

125
00:05:47,006 --> 00:05:48,000
To eat, of course.

126
00:05:48,080 --> 00:05:49,000
Who are we eating with?

127
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:49,870
You'll see.

128
00:05:50,607 --> 00:05:52,167
- Let's go.
- Not if I don't know them.

129
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:54,510
Let's go. Come on.

130
00:05:54,630 --> 00:05:55,560
Hurry, hurry!

131
00:05:56,430 --> 00:05:57,920
The pace is really fast.

132
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:58,780
Come on in.

133
00:05:58,800 --> 00:06:00,000
We're counting on you.

134
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:03,480
Director Ding!

135
00:06:05,190 --> 00:06:06,920
Director, this is...

136
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:09,160
Director Feng, the provincial troupe.

137
00:06:09,630 --> 00:06:12,120
A famous Qinqiang opera director indeed!

138
00:06:12,630 --> 00:06:13,950
Nice to meet you.

139
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:15,040
And you are?

140
00:06:15,950 --> 00:06:17,480
I'm Chu Jiahe's mother.

141
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:20,430
Excuse me. I need to use the restroom.

142
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:21,880
Jiahe...

143
00:06:22,510 --> 00:06:23,800
Please sit. Come on over.

144
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:24,950
I won't stay.

145
00:06:24,950 --> 00:06:26,360
I really have plans tonight.

146
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:27,800
Director Ding didn't explain clearly.

147
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:29,270
I know the whole situation.

148
00:06:29,630 --> 00:06:31,390
Let's just say we met today.

149
00:06:31,390 --> 00:06:33,040
We'll catch up another time, okay?

150
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:34,430
I... You...

151
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:37,630
Take care, Director Feng.

152
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:40,430
Director Ding, this...

153
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:42,750
That's just how he is.

154
00:06:42,750 --> 00:06:43,590
Weirdo.

155
00:06:43,830 --> 00:06:44,750
He's a director.

156
00:06:44,750 --> 00:06:46,600
Right, right. Please, sit.

157
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:47,750
I won't stay either.

158
00:06:47,750 --> 00:06:48,600
I'll go make sure

159
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:49,830
he doesn't talk nonsense.

160
00:06:50,390 --> 00:06:52,720
Director Ding,
let me get you a ride back.

161
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:54,190
No need, it's just a short walk.

162
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:56,800
I also brought some gifts
for you in my car.

163
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:59,830
I'll have my driver
drop them at your house.

164
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:01,750
You really shouldn't have.

165
00:07:01,830 --> 00:07:02,750
I'll get going now.

166
00:07:02,750 --> 00:07:04,630
Alright, take care.

167
00:07:04,630 --> 00:07:05,470
Okay, okay.

168
00:07:07,830 --> 00:07:08,670
They blew it.

169
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:21,160
I was handling things for you.

170
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:22,270
And you hid in the bathroom!

171
00:07:22,270 --> 00:07:23,390
What's wrong with you?

172
00:07:23,950 --> 00:07:25,480
Why did you bring Director Feng here?

173
00:07:25,950 --> 00:07:27,800
He has the power to decide
on the actress.

174
00:07:28,830 --> 00:07:30,390
You don't know him at all.

175
00:07:30,630 --> 00:07:32,560
He's a nerdy intellectual.

176
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:33,950
He hates this kind of stuff.

177
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:36,430
Doing this will only backfire.

178
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:37,560
You...

179
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:42,950
Anything can be worked out.

180
00:07:43,510 --> 00:07:44,350
We'll take it slow.

181
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:45,950
We need to think this through.

182
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:49,190
About that blind date I mentioned,

183
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:51,510
the matchmaker got back to me.

184
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:52,480
You'll meet next week.

185
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:54,200
I'm not going.

186
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:57,070
Who do you think you are?

187
00:07:57,310 --> 00:07:59,270
This young man is a rare catch.

188
00:07:59,270 --> 00:08:01,720
His dad is a Chief
at your Department of Finance.

189
00:08:01,800 --> 00:08:04,430
He decides your funding.

190
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:07,310
Date him, and the lead is yours.

191
00:08:07,950 --> 00:08:09,160
I can earn it myself.

192
00:08:10,830 --> 00:08:13,120
Chu Jiahe, don't be ungrateful.

193
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:14,480
I spent real money

194
00:08:14,510 --> 00:08:17,120
and called in so many favors

195
00:08:17,950 --> 00:08:19,360
to get you that B role.

196
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:22,160
You think you got it on talent?

197
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:24,510
You've worked hard enough at opera.

198
00:08:24,510 --> 00:08:26,750
Life isn't just about singing opera.

199
00:08:27,430 --> 00:08:28,560
You blockhead.

200
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:32,360
I call the shots in my own life.

201
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:33,200
You...

202
00:08:33,830 --> 00:08:35,120
Chu Jiahe, you...

203
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:36,560
Come on, fill them up.

204
00:08:36,560 --> 00:08:38,480
Let's get this business sorted, guys.

205
00:08:38,733 --> 00:08:39,720
Make sure to get it done.

206
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:40,560
No problem.

207
00:08:40,680 --> 00:08:41,560
Wait.

208
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:42,440
I'm taking off.

209
00:08:51,630 --> 00:08:52,470
Swan.

210
00:08:54,390 --> 00:08:55,680
Why are you everywhere?

211
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:59,920
You failed at treating Director Feng

212
00:08:59,920 --> 00:09:00,950
to dinner.

213
00:09:03,040 --> 00:09:04,190
What's it to you?

214
00:09:04,190 --> 00:09:05,360
How is it not my business?

215
00:09:06,310 --> 00:09:07,260
You plan to treat him.

216
00:09:07,260 --> 00:09:08,100
If you get the part,

217
00:09:08,100 --> 00:09:09,430
won't our Qin'e lose it?

218
00:09:16,390 --> 00:09:17,230
What's so funny?

219
00:09:17,630 --> 00:09:18,630
You.

220
00:09:19,800 --> 00:09:22,040
You think I'm Yi Qin'e's only rival?

221
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:24,360
I'm out of You Xi Hu now.

222
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:25,680
But she is still in the play.

223
00:09:25,800 --> 00:09:27,800
The one outshining her now is Gong Lili.

224
00:09:29,830 --> 00:09:31,190
I know that.

225
00:09:31,240 --> 00:09:33,190
What do you even know?

226
00:09:33,190 --> 00:09:34,040
Look at you.

227
00:09:34,050 --> 00:09:35,430
You're always talking

228
00:09:35,430 --> 00:09:36,270
with everyone,

229
00:09:36,270 --> 00:09:38,040
buying Rou Jia Mo and soda.

230
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:39,240
What good does that do?

231
00:09:39,390 --> 00:09:40,430
Then what should I do?

232
00:09:40,430 --> 00:09:41,630
Use your connections.

233
00:09:41,800 --> 00:09:43,360
And find the key person.

234
00:09:44,240 --> 00:09:46,240
Have you figured out who runs

235
00:09:46,240 --> 00:09:47,430
the You Xi Hu crew now?

236
00:09:52,160 --> 00:09:53,240
Tell me more about it.

237
00:09:55,600 --> 00:09:57,909
Do you know why Gong Lili never falls?

238
00:09:57,920 --> 00:09:59,106
Because she and Director Feng

239
00:09:59,117 --> 00:10:01,270
studied under the Qinqiang opera master,
Ms. Li.

240
00:10:01,800 --> 00:10:02,886
They're fellow apprentices.

241
00:10:03,160 --> 00:10:04,190
Surely, he'd help her.

242
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:07,800
That's all I can say.

243
00:10:08,030 --> 00:10:09,360
Figure out the rest yourself.

244
00:10:18,150 --> 00:10:20,600
Pulling strings is my forte.

245
00:10:54,720 --> 00:10:55,790
No, no, no.

246
00:10:58,630 --> 00:10:59,550
That's not right.

247
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:01,550
Come on, let's try it again.

248
00:11:01,550 --> 00:11:02,550
One more time. Come on.

249
00:11:03,510 --> 00:11:04,350
Let's go.

250
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:19,320
Still not right.

251
00:11:20,510 --> 00:11:21,390
Come on, come on.

252
00:11:21,390 --> 00:11:22,550
Again, again. Let's go.

253
00:11:22,550 --> 00:11:23,400
What's wrong today?

254
00:11:23,410 --> 00:11:25,440
Director, what's wrong with it?

255
00:11:36,390 --> 00:11:37,550
Let's call it a day.

256
00:11:38,790 --> 00:11:40,600
Go rest. We'll resume tomorrow.

257
00:11:42,062 --> 00:11:43,052
What are you doing after?

258
00:11:43,063 --> 00:11:43,840
Director, your cup.

259
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:45,440
Playing mahjong. What else?

260
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:48,320
I'm off.

261
00:11:52,390 --> 00:11:53,720
Come back when you're rested.

262
00:11:53,790 --> 00:11:54,670
I'm fine.

263
00:11:55,150 --> 00:11:56,270
I'm heading out now.

264
00:11:56,670 --> 00:11:57,630
Take it easy practicing.

265
00:11:57,630 --> 00:11:58,470
Okay.

266
00:12:03,750 --> 00:12:04,590
Jiahe.

267
00:12:05,080 --> 00:12:05,986
Are you feeling better?

268
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:08,080
Much better.

269
00:12:08,390 --> 00:12:10,240
Can you do You Xi Hu this time?

270
00:12:11,870 --> 00:12:13,320
I might still need to rest.

271
00:12:14,030 --> 00:12:15,670
Stop making small talk.

272
00:12:15,670 --> 00:12:17,200
Go do your own thing.

273
00:12:17,750 --> 00:12:18,660
Your issues are

274
00:12:18,671 --> 00:12:19,904
way more troublesome than mine.

275
00:12:43,840 --> 00:12:46,440
Why are you sitting here all alone?

276
00:12:49,750 --> 00:12:52,840
I was just thinking of Director Gu.

277
00:12:55,030 --> 00:12:57,080
Did you bond over the fights or what?

278
00:12:59,150 --> 00:13:01,200
I feel like he's another version of me.

279
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:04,790
Whenever I get too confident

280
00:13:04,790 --> 00:13:06,030
and sure of success,

281
00:13:06,030 --> 00:13:08,670
he always plays devil's advocate.

282
00:13:09,390 --> 00:13:11,080
If I say east,

283
00:13:11,240 --> 00:13:12,960
he insists on west.

284
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:15,320
But that also gives me

285
00:13:15,320 --> 00:13:16,360
another perspective.

286
00:13:17,120 --> 00:13:20,150
Now, two people are sharing one role.

287
00:13:21,360 --> 00:13:23,150
That's not what I want either.

288
00:13:31,150 --> 00:13:32,630
Then what do you want?

289
00:13:33,480 --> 00:13:35,910
I just want to perfect the play.

290
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:39,000
You...

291
00:13:43,270 --> 00:13:45,200
Another opera nut.

292
00:13:47,790 --> 00:13:48,960
Rock, paper, scissors!

293
00:13:50,630 --> 00:13:52,600
You just love playing here, huh?

294
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:53,840
Excuse me, coming through.

295
00:13:59,100 --> 00:13:59,960
Listen to that sizzle.

296
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:00,840
Stir-frying?

297
00:14:00,840 --> 00:14:01,680
You're back!

298
00:14:04,670 --> 00:14:05,510
Director Feng.

299
00:14:06,030 --> 00:14:07,630
- Hello, hello!
- Hello.

300
00:14:07,630 --> 00:14:08,480
I'm Liu Hongbing.

301
00:14:08,840 --> 00:14:10,270
Yi Qin'e's boyfriend.

302
00:14:11,320 --> 00:14:12,390
About Yi Qin'e's matter,

303
00:14:12,390 --> 00:14:13,480
I can assure you...

304
00:14:13,480 --> 00:14:14,910
Right, right. Let's talk inside.

305
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:16,360
Let's talk inside. Inside.

306
00:14:16,360 --> 00:14:17,200
Why push me?

307
00:14:17,360 --> 00:14:19,270
Director Feng, on behalf of Qin'e,

308
00:14:19,270 --> 00:14:21,720
I brought you a little gift today.

309
00:14:23,150 --> 00:14:24,630
I won't say this twice.

310
00:14:24,630 --> 00:14:25,870
Take your things and get out.

311
00:14:25,870 --> 00:14:27,750
Director Feng, don't be like that.

312
00:14:28,030 --> 00:14:29,870
I'm just here to drop by and say hello.

313
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:30,910
Besides,

314
00:14:30,910 --> 00:14:33,510
Qin'e is your student, right?

315
00:14:33,510 --> 00:14:35,360
Young man, if you're here

316
00:14:35,360 --> 00:14:37,000
to pull strings,

317
00:14:37,030 --> 00:14:38,840
you've come to the wrong place.

318
00:14:39,240 --> 00:14:41,750
He's an artist, so high and mighty.

319
00:14:41,750 --> 00:14:43,320
He won't even look

320
00:14:43,320 --> 00:14:44,480
at your cheap little gifts.

321
00:14:44,600 --> 00:14:45,910
What are you talking about?

322
00:14:45,910 --> 00:14:47,030
Just drop it, okay?

323
00:14:47,030 --> 00:14:48,120
So what if I said it?

324
00:14:48,120 --> 00:14:49,360
She's right.

325
00:14:49,630 --> 00:14:51,270
This stuff really isn't presentable.

326
00:14:51,270 --> 00:14:52,960
I'll bring something better next time.

327
00:14:53,200 --> 00:14:54,240
But I think you have

328
00:14:54,320 --> 00:14:55,960
some misunderstandings about Qin'e.

329
00:14:56,550 --> 00:14:58,120
What misunderstanding?

330
00:14:58,120 --> 00:15:00,000
Yi Qin'e's vocal style is flawed.

331
00:15:00,456 --> 00:15:01,786
I'm not targeting her personally.

332
00:15:01,797 --> 00:15:03,157
I just want the best for the play.

333
00:15:03,360 --> 00:15:04,440
As for the troupe's plans,

334
00:15:04,440 --> 00:15:06,550
I can't decide that alone.

335
00:15:06,550 --> 00:15:08,000
Just get out of here.

336
00:15:08,120 --> 00:15:10,750
My visit today isn't about that.

337
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:12,150
I just came

338
00:15:12,600 --> 00:15:14,910
to make friends with you.

339
00:15:15,150 --> 00:15:16,630
I don't need any friends.

340
00:15:16,630 --> 00:15:17,250
Just go.

341
00:15:17,261 --> 00:15:18,910
- Take your stuff.
- Don't be like that.

342
00:15:18,910 --> 00:15:20,105
- Director Feng.
- In life...

343
00:15:20,116 --> 00:15:20,960
Director Feng!

344
00:15:21,550 --> 00:15:23,390
Can't you hear? Your dad threw up.

345
00:15:24,030 --> 00:15:24,910
I heard it.

346
00:15:25,720 --> 00:15:27,750
See? Doesn't this work out perfectly?

347
00:15:27,750 --> 00:15:29,270
Leave the art to the artists.

348
00:15:29,270 --> 00:15:31,270
Let me handle the daily chores.

349
00:15:31,270 --> 00:15:33,320
Uncle, Uncle, oh you...

350
00:15:33,320 --> 00:15:34,320
You threw up everything.

351
00:15:34,750 --> 00:15:35,960
You just need a quick wipe.

352
00:15:35,960 --> 00:15:37,030
I'll wipe it off for you.

353
00:15:37,030 --> 00:15:38,200
- Mom is doing laundry.
- Go.

354
00:15:38,200 --> 00:15:39,660
I'll get this rice off his chest.

355
00:15:39,680 --> 00:15:40,520
- Get out!
- Simple.

356
00:15:40,520 --> 00:15:41,380
Alright, get out.

357
00:15:41,390 --> 00:15:42,310
You clean him up then.

358
00:15:43,550 --> 00:15:44,390
Uncle, you...

359
00:15:54,790 --> 00:15:55,630
Ma'am.

360
00:15:56,910 --> 00:15:57,750
The kid...

361
00:15:58,630 --> 00:15:59,470
Come here.

362
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:01,550
Have some milk.

363
00:16:02,750 --> 00:16:04,510
Have some milk.

364
00:16:05,030 --> 00:16:06,630
You can't even feed a baby.

365
00:16:06,630 --> 00:16:07,670
Here, give the baby to me.

366
00:16:09,550 --> 00:16:10,750
Come, I've got you.

367
00:16:10,750 --> 00:16:12,600
I'll take you for some milk.

368
00:16:12,600 --> 00:16:13,440
Come here.

369
00:16:13,870 --> 00:16:15,270
Let me hold you.

370
00:16:15,270 --> 00:16:16,110
No more crying.

371
00:16:16,360 --> 00:16:17,790
Drink your milk.

372
00:16:22,550 --> 00:16:23,390
Look at this mess.

373
00:16:23,870 --> 00:16:25,720
Come on, let's tidy up.

374
00:16:26,200 --> 00:16:28,270
Who usually cleans up around here?

375
00:16:29,790 --> 00:16:31,080
What's your name?

376
00:16:32,510 --> 00:16:33,550
I'm talking to you.

377
00:16:35,910 --> 00:16:37,360
What? You can't speak?

378
00:16:40,870 --> 00:16:42,030
Really?

379
00:16:45,510 --> 00:16:47,000
Do your homework.

380
00:16:50,360 --> 00:16:51,380
Why haven't you left yet?

381
00:16:51,480 --> 00:16:52,360
You should go.

382
00:16:52,370 --> 00:16:53,230
Why should he go?

383
00:16:53,240 --> 00:16:54,510
He's helping with the chores.

384
00:16:54,510 --> 00:16:55,440
Can't you see that?

385
00:16:55,440 --> 00:16:56,816
You do nothing around the house.

386
00:16:56,910 --> 00:16:58,130
If anyone's leaving, it's you.

387
00:16:58,600 --> 00:17:01,390
Exactly. Director Feng, do some work.

388
00:17:03,320 --> 00:17:04,600
You two should live together.

389
00:17:07,360 --> 00:17:09,550
Ma'am, he's just angry.

390
00:17:09,550 --> 00:17:11,840
Artists have quirks.

391
00:17:12,000 --> 00:17:14,320
He has quirks? So do I!

392
00:17:18,080 --> 00:17:19,600
Why did you stop? Do your homework.

393
00:17:22,360 --> 00:17:23,960
You've had a hard question?

394
00:17:25,030 --> 00:17:25,960
Let me take a look.

395
00:17:28,870 --> 00:17:30,550
It takes three hours

396
00:17:30,960 --> 00:17:33,360
to fill a pool with water.

397
00:17:33,870 --> 00:17:36,240
It takes four hours to drain.

398
00:17:36,240 --> 00:17:37,630
If filling and draining...

399
00:17:38,240 --> 00:17:39,750
Why do they still have this problem?

400
00:17:39,750 --> 00:17:40,870
I did this when I was a kid.

401
00:17:40,870 --> 00:17:42,320
It made me so mad.

402
00:17:42,670 --> 00:17:44,480
I'll complain to the education board.

403
00:17:44,480 --> 00:17:45,390
Filling and draining

404
00:17:45,390 --> 00:17:46,390
is a total waste.

405
00:17:47,000 --> 00:17:48,390
Director Feng, the fire's out again.

406
00:17:48,390 --> 00:17:49,600
How am I supposed to cook?

407
00:17:50,360 --> 00:17:51,960
What are you yelling about?

408
00:17:52,200 --> 00:17:53,750
I'll light it later if it's out.

409
00:17:53,750 --> 00:17:55,030
Why all the shouting?

410
00:17:55,120 --> 00:17:56,790
So what if I'm yelling?

411
00:17:56,870 --> 00:17:58,270
Have you lifted a finger?

412
00:17:58,390 --> 00:17:59,360
There's a guest here.

413
00:17:59,360 --> 00:18:01,080
Why are you being so loud?

414
00:18:01,670 --> 00:18:02,750
You realize that now?

415
00:18:03,270 --> 00:18:04,270
I'll yell if I want to.

416
00:18:06,320 --> 00:18:08,480
When the troupe gave raises and titles,

417
00:18:08,480 --> 00:18:09,390
where were you?

418
00:18:10,600 --> 00:18:11,613
Why are you backing away?

419
00:18:11,680 --> 00:18:12,680
Why?

420
00:18:13,000 --> 00:18:15,200
Why bring this up now?

421
00:18:15,360 --> 00:18:16,550
Because I want to!

422
00:18:16,550 --> 00:18:17,390
I must be cursed

423
00:18:17,400 --> 00:18:18,960
with terrible luck

424
00:18:18,960 --> 00:18:20,200
to end up with a loser like you.

425
00:18:20,270 --> 00:18:22,630
When I was a Xiaodan
at the County Troupe,

426
00:18:22,630 --> 00:18:24,080
I had so many suitors.

427
00:18:24,720 --> 00:18:26,150
I was blind to choose you.

428
00:18:28,240 --> 00:18:30,480
Then go back to the County Troupe.

429
00:18:37,320 --> 00:18:38,160
Don't be afraid.

430
00:18:39,000 --> 00:18:39,840
It's okay.

431
00:18:42,270 --> 00:18:43,480
I'm hungry.

432
00:18:44,640 --> 00:18:45,480
You can talk!

433
00:18:46,920 --> 00:18:48,510
Uncle, my mom won't let me

434
00:18:48,510 --> 00:18:50,310
speak in front of others.

435
00:18:59,750 --> 00:19:01,750
I'll ask your mom to cook for you later.

436
00:19:02,160 --> 00:19:03,480
Finish your homework first.

437
00:19:08,070 --> 00:19:08,910
Director Feng.

438
00:19:10,310 --> 00:19:11,150
Director Feng,

439
00:19:11,680 --> 00:19:12,720
let me say a few words.

440
00:19:13,110 --> 00:19:14,240
I'll leave right after.

441
00:19:17,000 --> 00:19:18,640
As for Qin'e's vocal style,

442
00:19:19,510 --> 00:19:21,880
she has really worked hard.

443
00:19:22,310 --> 00:19:24,920
She listens to Li Zhengmin's tapes daily

444
00:19:25,110 --> 00:19:27,640
and rehearses with a teacher every day.

445
00:19:28,880 --> 00:19:31,240
Everyone can see her progress.

446
00:19:32,750 --> 00:19:33,750
To her,

447
00:19:34,350 --> 00:19:38,030
singing opera means the world.

448
00:19:40,830 --> 00:19:42,070
I'm done.

449
00:19:50,920 --> 00:19:51,760
Director Feng.

450
00:19:53,830 --> 00:19:54,830
Director Feng?

451
00:19:55,550 --> 00:19:57,550
Singing opera

452
00:19:58,030 --> 00:20:02,350
doesn't mean a thing in real life.

453
00:20:09,480 --> 00:20:12,350
Just take your things and go.

454
00:20:13,550 --> 00:20:15,000
Don't make this hard for me.

455
00:20:15,310 --> 00:20:18,000
I'm begging you, alright?

456
00:20:26,960 --> 00:20:28,590
More dried shrimp, no cilantro.

457
00:20:28,590 --> 00:20:29,480
Okay, okay.

458
00:20:29,880 --> 00:20:31,080
Sir,

459
00:20:31,200 --> 00:20:32,350
four Rou Jia Mo, please.

460
00:20:32,350 --> 00:20:34,000
Sure thing, just a moment.

461
00:20:34,550 --> 00:20:35,390
Sir!

462
00:20:35,830 --> 00:20:37,480
Four wontons, one non-spicy.

463
00:20:37,510 --> 00:20:39,160
Okay, just a sec. Coming right up.

464
00:20:39,510 --> 00:20:40,510
Hurry up and cook!

465
00:20:40,510 --> 00:20:42,030
You might not eat, but others do!

466
00:20:42,030 --> 00:20:43,720
Your dad's rolling his eyes from hunger.

467
00:20:44,030 --> 00:20:45,960
Stop rushing me. I'll make it.

468
00:20:45,960 --> 00:20:47,880
I need the fire to heat up first.

469
00:20:48,030 --> 00:20:48,870
Wait.

470
00:20:51,640 --> 00:20:53,720
Who poured water in my stove?

471
00:20:54,310 --> 00:20:55,480
An uncle did it.

472
00:20:55,480 --> 00:20:56,830
He told you to eat this.

473
00:21:07,480 --> 00:21:08,590
The official show

474
00:21:08,590 --> 00:21:10,550
of You Xi Hu is starting soon.

475
00:21:10,790 --> 00:21:12,960
Today at the rehearsal, we're very lucky

476
00:21:12,960 --> 00:21:15,400
to have Qinqiang opera master Ms. Li

477
00:21:15,480 --> 00:21:17,720
and many veteran Qinqiang opera artists

478
00:21:17,720 --> 00:21:19,310
to help us evaluate the performance.

479
00:21:19,310 --> 00:21:20,200
Let's welcome them.

480
00:21:25,240 --> 00:21:26,680
Okay, get ready for the show.

481
00:21:57,550 --> 00:22:01,550
♪The wrongfully dead♪

482
00:22:01,550 --> 00:22:03,200
Very good, very good.

483
00:22:17,070 --> 00:22:32,960
♪Vengeful spirits filled with rage♪

484
00:22:43,030 --> 00:22:44,880
She truly is your top student.

485
00:22:45,110 --> 00:22:46,000
Please, enjoy the show.

486
00:22:46,000 --> 00:22:55,720
♪The stars and moon are dim;
the wind and dew are cold♪

487
00:23:51,000 --> 00:23:54,160
♪I will keep you safe♪

488
00:24:04,790 --> 00:24:06,830
♪Where are you going♪

489
00:24:49,640 --> 00:24:51,960
Ms. Li, please give us your feedback.

490
00:24:56,310 --> 00:24:57,310
Lili, you stay.

491
00:24:57,640 --> 00:24:59,110
Everyone else, off the stage.

492
00:25:00,640 --> 00:25:01,680
It's okay; you go first.

493
00:25:04,160 --> 00:25:05,590
Bring the girl doing fire breathing

494
00:25:06,110 --> 00:25:07,960
and Woyu

495
00:25:07,960 --> 00:25:08,960
up here to me.

496
00:25:11,030 --> 00:25:11,870
Go!

497
00:25:12,510 --> 00:25:13,350
Qin'e,

498
00:25:14,640 --> 00:25:16,070
Director Feng wants you on stage.

499
00:25:28,960 --> 00:25:31,790
Why do you

500
00:25:32,440 --> 00:25:36,880
need two actresses to play Li Huiniang?

501
00:25:38,030 --> 00:25:40,160
The old opera hasn't been back for long.

502
00:25:40,310 --> 00:25:41,880
The actresses in the troupe right now

503
00:25:41,880 --> 00:25:43,590
can't pull it off alone.

504
00:25:43,960 --> 00:25:46,590
Then they should keep practicing.

505
00:25:52,240 --> 00:25:55,200
When I saw you do fire breathing,

506
00:25:55,750 --> 00:25:58,270
for a moment, I thought I saw

507
00:25:58,510 --> 00:26:00,110
the Nandan from Beishan,

508
00:26:01,110 --> 00:26:02,350
Gou Cunzhong.

509
00:26:02,830 --> 00:26:04,680
Master Gou is my master.

510
00:26:06,640 --> 00:26:08,000
No wonder.

511
00:26:08,750 --> 00:26:11,240
Your Woyu has his style too.

512
00:26:13,750 --> 00:26:17,640
His essence is
three long bursts of fire.

513
00:26:18,030 --> 00:26:19,720
Why didn't I see you do it?

514
00:26:20,030 --> 00:26:21,310
I haven't learned it yet.

515
00:26:24,200 --> 00:26:25,040
Lili,

516
00:26:25,590 --> 00:26:26,440
you step down first.

517
00:26:27,920 --> 00:26:29,590
Lili, step down first.

518
00:26:34,110 --> 00:26:37,110
Sing a part of Gui Yuan without music.

519
00:26:39,790 --> 00:26:50,030
♪So bitter♪

520
00:26:59,640 --> 00:27:00,480
Qin'e.

521
00:27:00,960 --> 00:27:01,800
Congratulations!

522
00:27:01,920 --> 00:27:03,640
Your friend didn't lie to me.

523
00:27:03,880 --> 00:27:05,720
You did an amazing job today.

524
00:27:05,720 --> 00:27:06,920
You must have worked hard.

525
00:27:07,160 --> 00:27:08,200
What friend?

526
00:27:08,480 --> 00:27:09,320
I mean

527
00:27:09,550 --> 00:27:12,000
that young guy with the curly hair.

528
00:27:12,550 --> 00:27:13,830
He went to see you?

529
00:27:13,960 --> 00:27:17,480
The fire breathing looked great
from offstage.

530
00:27:17,630 --> 00:27:18,600
You did great.

531
00:27:18,880 --> 00:27:19,830
I didn't do well.

532
00:27:20,590 --> 00:27:22,270
My breath was stuck in my chest.

533
00:27:22,270 --> 00:27:23,460
I wasn't relaxed enough.

534
00:27:25,510 --> 00:27:28,070
I think it's not just about breathing.

535
00:27:28,270 --> 00:27:31,310
It's also how you build the character.

536
00:27:31,550 --> 00:27:33,920
Of course, I'm no fire breathing expert.

537
00:27:33,920 --> 00:27:36,310
But from an acting perspective,

538
00:27:36,590 --> 00:27:37,550
you can try

539
00:27:37,700 --> 00:27:40,300
digging deep within yourself.

540
00:27:40,300 --> 00:27:42,340
Put yourself in Li Hui Niang's mind.

541
00:27:42,860 --> 00:27:44,380
Think about Li Hui Niang.

542
00:27:44,700 --> 00:27:48,180
She was forced apart from her lover,

543
00:27:48,180 --> 00:27:49,460
separated by death.

544
00:27:49,580 --> 00:27:51,220
They could never see each other again.

545
00:27:51,220 --> 00:27:52,820
How do you think that feels?

546
00:27:54,260 --> 00:27:56,500
That kind of anger, sorrow,

547
00:27:56,500 --> 00:27:57,340
and regret.

548
00:27:57,580 --> 00:28:00,260
She's not just using breath
for fire breathing.

549
00:28:00,260 --> 00:28:01,740
She's expressing it with her heart.

550
00:28:04,380 --> 00:28:05,300
Thanks, Director Feng.

551
00:28:05,740 --> 00:28:06,580
No need.

552
00:28:07,180 --> 00:28:08,220
Think about it carefully.

553
00:28:16,220 --> 00:28:17,460
This kid's progress

554
00:28:17,460 --> 00:28:18,980
is clear for all to see.

555
00:28:18,980 --> 00:28:20,700
She improves almost every single day.

556
00:28:21,140 --> 00:28:23,060
Great personality too, never pushy.

557
00:28:23,120 --> 00:28:24,820
Look, I gave her
the cold shoulder before.

558
00:28:24,820 --> 00:28:25,940
She didn't even get mad.

559
00:28:26,420 --> 00:28:27,900
With such great fire breathing skills,

560
00:28:27,900 --> 00:28:30,300
she never showed off to the director.

561
00:28:30,420 --> 00:28:31,900
She's very calm and steady.

562
00:28:32,020 --> 00:28:34,340
Isn't that what we call a true master?

563
00:28:34,780 --> 00:28:35,620
Compared to her,

564
00:28:35,620 --> 00:28:37,300
I'm the petty one.

565
00:28:37,300 --> 00:28:38,540
But I wasn't targeting her.

566
00:28:39,180 --> 00:28:40,780
I rejected her

567
00:28:40,780 --> 00:28:42,140
because I rejected Gu Cunxiao.

568
00:28:42,660 --> 00:28:45,300
But this kid used her actions

569
00:28:45,300 --> 00:28:46,180
to completely

570
00:28:46,180 --> 00:28:48,060
change my mind.

571
00:28:51,020 --> 00:28:53,340
Troupe Leader, do you agree or not?

572
00:28:57,700 --> 00:28:59,500
Recasting someone like this

573
00:28:59,660 --> 00:29:01,460
could cause a huge uproar.

574
00:29:02,860 --> 00:29:03,780
For this kind of thing,

575
00:29:04,140 --> 00:29:06,620
why didn't you speak up earlier?

576
00:29:06,780 --> 00:29:08,060
I wanted to say it earlier,

577
00:29:08,060 --> 00:29:10,060
but I've been thinking about it too.

578
00:29:10,060 --> 00:29:11,020
I was hesitating.

579
00:29:11,020 --> 00:29:12,860
I was afraid you wouldn't accept it.

580
00:29:12,980 --> 00:29:15,300
But we're really running out of time.

581
00:29:18,340 --> 00:29:19,180
How about this?

582
00:29:20,780 --> 00:29:22,420
Let her just perform

583
00:29:22,420 --> 00:29:24,540
Sha Sheng and Gui Yuan.

584
00:29:25,540 --> 00:29:26,540
That way,

585
00:29:27,500 --> 00:29:29,340
it'll be easier for the team to accept.

586
00:29:32,460 --> 00:29:33,986
I'll announce it at rehearsal tomorrow.

587
00:29:34,180 --> 00:29:35,020
No, that won't work.

588
00:29:35,180 --> 00:29:36,500
You can't do it.

589
00:29:37,020 --> 00:29:37,900
This is something

590
00:29:38,790 --> 00:29:39,940
that I have to do.

591
00:29:41,380 --> 00:29:43,300
And I need to find the right moment.

592
00:29:47,100 --> 00:29:48,460
I've sung opera since I was a kid.

593
00:29:49,900 --> 00:29:50,860
Everyone told me

594
00:29:51,020 --> 00:29:52,380
to just focus on singing.

595
00:29:54,540 --> 00:29:55,540
For so many years,

596
00:29:55,860 --> 00:29:58,340
I've done nothing else but sing.

597
00:29:59,660 --> 00:30:01,340
Now, I can't even do that right.

598
00:30:01,980 --> 00:30:03,500
What else can I do?

599
00:30:08,500 --> 00:30:09,380
Stop crying.

600
00:30:10,700 --> 00:30:11,540
Lili,

601
00:30:12,220 --> 00:30:13,140
it's all my fault.

602
00:30:14,020 --> 00:30:14,900
Don't cry.

603
00:30:15,340 --> 00:30:16,500
When you cry like this,

604
00:30:16,540 --> 00:30:18,020
it breaks my heart too.

605
00:30:18,340 --> 00:30:20,900
The troupe can't do without you now.

606
00:30:21,140 --> 00:30:22,300
You're still the lead.

607
00:30:23,580 --> 00:30:24,860
I can't just let this go.

608
00:30:25,740 --> 00:30:27,460
Why should we let it go?

609
00:30:28,900 --> 00:30:30,060
We have to fight back.

610
00:30:30,700 --> 00:30:32,260
Watch how I show them who's boss.

611
00:30:34,020 --> 00:30:34,900
Just watch.

612
00:30:35,380 --> 00:30:38,460
(Rehearsal Hall)

613
00:30:51,940 --> 00:30:52,860
Yi Qin'e.

614
00:30:56,140 --> 00:30:57,420
So, you're Yi Qin'e.

615
00:30:58,460 --> 00:31:01,380
What did you do to Feng Zi

616
00:31:01,780 --> 00:31:03,060
and the cripple?

617
00:31:03,540 --> 00:31:04,380
What do you mean?

618
00:31:04,780 --> 00:31:05,660
What do I mean?

619
00:31:06,540 --> 00:31:07,580
What a surprise.

620
00:31:08,100 --> 00:31:09,940
A country bumpkin from the county,

621
00:31:10,340 --> 00:31:11,780
trying every trick

622
00:31:11,780 --> 00:31:13,500
to join the provincial troupe.

623
00:31:13,740 --> 00:31:14,980
What skills do you have?

624
00:31:15,780 --> 00:31:16,660
What do you want?

625
00:31:17,020 --> 00:31:18,580
What could I possibly want?

626
00:31:20,180 --> 00:31:21,580
Isn't she the one who does

627
00:31:21,580 --> 00:31:23,340
the Woyu best in our troupe?

628
00:31:24,140 --> 00:31:24,980
Come on.

629
00:31:27,780 --> 00:31:28,700
Do it right here.

630
00:31:28,980 --> 00:31:30,340
Let everyone see it.

631
00:31:30,860 --> 00:31:31,700
Come on.

632
00:31:32,180 --> 00:31:33,860
It's just a lousy Woyu.

633
00:31:33,900 --> 00:31:36,460
Why say my wife can't do it?

634
00:31:38,180 --> 00:31:39,180
Why?

635
00:31:39,580 --> 00:31:40,700
Did you see her practice

636
00:31:40,700 --> 00:31:41,700
in the room?

637
00:31:42,900 --> 00:31:44,060
I did!

638
00:31:44,780 --> 00:31:46,580
Is it easy for a woman to have a baby?

639
00:31:47,260 --> 00:31:48,100
Is it?

640
00:31:48,780 --> 00:31:50,660
Out-of-towners like you

641
00:31:51,100 --> 00:31:52,580
have made a mess of this troupe,

642
00:31:52,580 --> 00:31:53,660
ruining the Qinqiang opera

643
00:31:53,700 --> 00:31:54,780
and the heritage.

644
00:31:55,060 --> 00:31:56,060
Let me tell you.

645
00:31:56,380 --> 00:31:57,300
You'd better behave.

646
00:31:57,300 --> 00:31:58,260
If you cause trouble,

647
00:31:58,260 --> 00:31:59,260
I'll teach you a lesson.

648
00:32:00,070 --> 00:32:00,980
Master Pi.

649
00:32:00,980 --> 00:32:01,820
Step aside.

650
00:32:02,820 --> 00:32:04,580
Master Pi, we need to rehearse soon.

651
00:32:04,580 --> 00:32:05,420
No way.

652
00:32:05,620 --> 00:32:07,220
- What's wrong?
- No one is rehearsing.

653
00:32:07,231 --> 00:32:08,351
- What's wrong?
- Master Pi.

654
00:32:08,362 --> 00:32:09,986
- Get lost!
- The troupe leader is here.

655
00:32:09,997 --> 00:32:11,180
- Pi Liang.
- Crazy man.

656
00:32:11,340 --> 00:32:12,260
What are you doing?

657
00:32:12,700 --> 00:32:14,500
If you want to be fired, just say so.

658
00:32:15,420 --> 00:32:16,260
Troupe Leader.

659
00:32:17,620 --> 00:32:18,900
He's been possessed.

660
00:32:18,900 --> 00:32:19,806
Who's been possessed?

661
00:32:19,920 --> 00:32:20,920
Tell me!

662
00:32:21,100 --> 00:32:22,780
Have you been possessed too?

663
00:32:22,860 --> 00:32:23,820
Watch your mouth!

664
00:32:24,020 --> 00:32:25,140
You all saw that.

665
00:32:25,380 --> 00:32:27,500
This woman is something else.

666
00:32:27,700 --> 00:32:28,900
She's got tricks up her sleeve.

667
00:32:29,300 --> 00:32:30,940
Do you have a third eye or something?

668
00:32:31,060 --> 00:32:32,620
What makes you so special?

669
00:32:32,820 --> 00:32:34,540
Pi Liang, don't do anything stupid.

670
00:32:34,700 --> 00:32:36,060
Don't you dare touch her.

671
00:32:36,060 --> 00:32:38,060
Don't scare me, Lame Shan!

672
00:32:38,100 --> 00:32:39,140
So what if I touch her?

673
00:32:39,140 --> 00:32:40,340
He's insulting you.

674
00:32:41,300 --> 00:32:42,380
Yi Qin'e, run!

675
00:32:42,380 --> 00:32:43,340
Get out of my way! You!

676
00:32:43,340 --> 00:32:45,260
How dare you insult me? You wanna die?

677
00:32:45,860 --> 00:32:47,180
- Don't stop me!
- You brat!

678
00:32:47,340 --> 00:32:48,500
How dare you hit her?

679
00:32:50,620 --> 00:32:51,780
- Master Pi!
- Pi Liang!

680
00:32:51,900 --> 00:32:53,020
Where are you going?

681
00:32:54,100 --> 00:32:55,580
Pi Liang, you reckless fool!

682
00:32:56,740 --> 00:32:57,700
How dare you insult me?

683
00:32:57,860 --> 00:32:59,500
Get out of the way!

684
00:32:59,500 --> 00:33:00,340
Don't move!

685
00:33:00,576 --> 00:33:01,649
- Pi Liang!
- You're back.

686
00:33:01,660 --> 00:33:02,500
You're back.

687
00:33:48,300 --> 00:33:49,140
Uncle.

688
00:33:50,020 --> 00:33:50,860
You're here.

689
00:33:51,420 --> 00:33:52,900
More punctual than going to work.

690
00:33:53,500 --> 00:33:54,380
Grab a bite.

691
00:33:55,720 --> 00:33:56,620
Here's a sweet potato.

692
00:33:56,620 --> 00:33:57,460
Try it.

693
00:34:00,260 --> 00:34:02,140
How much can a girl eat anyway?

694
00:34:03,740 --> 00:34:05,180
Don't let the leaders see you.

695
00:34:05,540 --> 00:34:07,220
- That's going too far.
- Yeah.

696
00:34:07,220 --> 00:34:09,300
Getting violent in the practice room!

697
00:34:09,300 --> 00:34:10,780
Luckily, Jiahe held him back.

698
00:34:10,780 --> 00:34:11,620
Anyway,

699
00:34:13,220 --> 00:34:15,660
we can't let this go.

700
00:34:15,860 --> 00:34:17,940
Who knows what he'll do next time?

701
00:34:19,140 --> 00:34:19,980
Yi Qin'e,

702
00:34:20,420 --> 00:34:22,020
you have to take a stand.

703
00:34:22,180 --> 00:34:23,020
Exactly.

704
00:34:23,020 --> 00:34:24,900
They're clearly bullying us outsiders.

705
00:34:24,900 --> 00:34:26,420
- Right
- Exactly.

706
00:34:26,540 --> 00:34:27,860
Listen to me, it's pure bullying.

707
00:34:29,380 --> 00:34:30,740
You moved the rehearsal here?

708
00:34:31,700 --> 00:34:32,580
Perfect timing.

709
00:34:33,700 --> 00:34:34,540
Look

710
00:34:34,660 --> 00:34:35,980
at this solid wood floor.

711
00:34:36,540 --> 00:34:37,740
How's the room now?

712
00:34:37,740 --> 00:34:39,060
You're still acting so pleased.

713
00:34:39,580 --> 00:34:41,620
Yi Qin'e almost got beaten up today.

714
00:34:43,340 --> 00:34:44,180
What happened?

715
00:34:46,660 --> 00:34:47,580
Who did it?

716
00:34:47,660 --> 00:34:48,620
No one.

717
00:34:50,220 --> 00:34:51,060
Who was it?

718
00:34:51,100 --> 00:34:52,500
None of your business. Stop asking.

719
00:34:54,780 --> 00:34:56,260
Fine. I'll find out myself.

720
00:34:56,660 --> 00:34:58,460
Find out what? Don't go.

721
00:34:59,300 --> 00:35:01,060
We can't just take this lying down.

722
00:35:02,700 --> 00:35:03,540
I'm fine.

723
00:35:04,020 --> 00:35:05,620
Tell me. I'll break his bones.

724
00:35:05,620 --> 00:35:06,900
She's fine for now,

725
00:35:07,180 --> 00:35:08,500
but it's only temporary.

726
00:35:09,500 --> 00:35:10,780
Qin'e is right, though.

727
00:35:11,020 --> 00:35:12,580
You can't go beating him up.

728
00:35:12,580 --> 00:35:14,420
If you start a fight, you're at fault.

729
00:35:14,860 --> 00:35:17,660
If you're in trouble,
who protects Yi Qin'e?

730
00:35:17,660 --> 00:35:18,500
Exactly.

731
00:35:25,780 --> 00:35:26,660
What happened?

732
00:35:27,140 --> 00:35:28,060
I didn't know.

733
00:35:28,060 --> 00:35:30,500
As I said, my business
isn't your concern.

734
00:35:31,660 --> 00:35:33,860
It's the A role of Li Hui Niang.

735
00:35:33,980 --> 00:35:35,420
She can't compete with Yi Qin'e.

736
00:35:35,660 --> 00:35:37,180
- So her husband
- Stop, Jiahe.

737
00:35:37,180 --> 00:35:38,940
made a huge scene at the troupe today.

738
00:35:38,940 --> 00:35:40,300
- Stop it.
- He tried to hit her.

739
00:35:40,300 --> 00:35:41,660
- Please stop.
- Yi Qin'e.

740
00:35:44,380 --> 00:35:46,260
You're way too nice, you know?

741
00:35:48,100 --> 00:35:49,060
Qin'e, listen to me.

742
00:35:49,060 --> 00:35:51,180
Just rest up. No need to rush back.

743
00:35:51,180 --> 00:35:52,020
Exactly.

744
00:35:53,140 --> 00:35:54,580
I've been wanting to leave for ages.

745
00:35:56,660 --> 00:35:57,780
This is outrageous.

746
00:35:57,820 --> 00:35:59,540
Why look down on us outsiders?

747
00:35:59,660 --> 00:36:00,980
What's wrong with us?

748
00:36:02,500 --> 00:36:03,620
Remember what I said.

749
00:36:03,700 --> 00:36:05,380
If anyone calls you to rehearse,

750
00:36:05,660 --> 00:36:06,500
don't go back.

751
00:36:07,220 --> 00:36:08,060
Promise me.

752
00:36:15,340 --> 00:36:16,180
You're leaving?

753
00:36:25,340 --> 00:36:26,780
Do you have something to tell me?

754
00:36:31,820 --> 00:36:33,900
It seems gifting Director Feng worked.

755
00:36:34,540 --> 00:36:35,380
What gift?

756
00:36:36,740 --> 00:36:38,420
Qin'e is just a good singer.

757
00:36:38,880 --> 00:36:40,146
What does it have to do with me?

758
00:36:40,500 --> 00:36:41,900
Fine, guess I shouldn't have cared.

759
00:36:44,340 --> 00:36:45,380
Thanks for today.

760
00:36:50,660 --> 00:36:52,180
Actually, it wasn't just for her.

761
00:36:52,580 --> 00:36:53,940
To be honest with you,

762
00:36:53,980 --> 00:36:55,673
I just wanted to use this to show

763
00:36:55,684 --> 00:36:56,673
those people in Chang'an

764
00:36:56,684 --> 00:36:57,700
where our bottom line is,

765
00:36:57,780 --> 00:36:59,540
or we'll just keep
getting pushed around.

766
00:37:14,020 --> 00:37:15,180
About the strike,

767
00:37:15,660 --> 00:37:16,780
you didn't mean it, did you?

768
00:37:17,620 --> 00:37:19,020
You just said it for Qin'e to hear.

769
00:37:19,980 --> 00:37:21,140
If you were serious,

770
00:37:21,900 --> 00:37:23,013
I suggest you think it over.

771
00:37:25,100 --> 00:37:25,980
What do you mean?

772
00:37:26,780 --> 00:37:28,180
The show is starting soon.

773
00:37:28,180 --> 00:37:30,500
They'll definitely smooth things over.

774
00:37:30,500 --> 00:37:32,220
Harmony is what matters, right?

775
00:37:33,820 --> 00:37:35,900
I didn't realize you were so spineless.

776
00:37:37,140 --> 00:37:37,980
Is that so?

777
00:37:38,860 --> 00:37:39,780
I didn't realize

778
00:37:39,780 --> 00:37:41,260
you were so scheming.

779
00:37:42,940 --> 00:37:44,140
Make yourself clear.

780
00:37:51,060 --> 00:37:52,220
You have no part

781
00:37:53,380 --> 00:37:54,540
in You Xi Hu anyway.

782
00:37:54,900 --> 00:37:55,760
Right?

783
00:37:55,820 --> 00:37:56,780
Acting out of spite now?

784
00:37:56,780 --> 00:37:58,580
You're ruining it,
so no one can perform.

785
00:38:00,300 --> 00:38:01,180
Listen to me.

786
00:38:02,020 --> 00:38:03,260
Someone like you?

787
00:38:04,860 --> 00:38:06,260
Don't even think about it.

788
00:38:08,300 --> 00:38:09,140
Am I right?

789
00:38:15,900 --> 00:38:16,740
Right?

790
00:38:40,140 --> 00:38:40,980
Master Chen.

791
00:38:43,510 --> 00:38:44,360
What?

792
00:38:44,370 --> 00:38:46,180
Is Yi Qin'e okay?

793
00:38:47,300 --> 00:38:48,140
What's wrong?

794
00:38:48,980 --> 00:38:49,820
You don't know?

795
00:38:51,220 --> 00:38:52,060
What happened?

796
00:38:54,020 --> 00:38:54,860
Look what this is.

797
00:38:55,420 --> 00:38:56,280
A stun baton.

798
00:38:56,340 --> 00:38:57,420
What are you up to now?

799
00:38:57,420 --> 00:38:58,420
Starting tomorrow,

800
00:38:58,420 --> 00:38:59,820
I'll watch over your rehearsals.

801
00:38:59,820 --> 00:39:00,660
Don't worry.

802
00:39:00,860 --> 00:39:02,420
I don't want to rehearse for now.

803
00:39:03,540 --> 00:39:05,220
Why are you listening to Chu Jiahe?

804
00:39:05,300 --> 00:39:06,580
I'm not listening to her.

805
00:39:07,300 --> 00:39:08,340
You wouldn't understand.

806
00:39:09,660 --> 00:39:10,980
Why are you being so dumb?

807
00:39:10,980 --> 00:39:11,900
I'm not dumb.

808
00:39:12,620 --> 00:39:14,340
Do you know that she has an agenda?

809
00:39:14,940 --> 00:39:16,780
She urged me
to get Director Feng a gift.

810
00:39:16,900 --> 00:39:18,140
But when I went, I found out

811
00:39:18,260 --> 00:39:19,740
Director Feng hates that.

812
00:39:19,740 --> 00:39:20,980
She was clearly setting me up.

813
00:39:20,980 --> 00:39:22,709
Who told you
to get Director Feng a gift?

814
00:39:22,720 --> 00:39:24,209
Who told you to meddle in my business?

815
00:39:24,220 --> 00:39:25,980
Do you remember my Eight Rules?

816
00:39:26,260 --> 00:39:27,540
The situation has changed.

817
00:39:27,540 --> 00:39:29,020
Besides, I did it for you.

818
00:39:30,080 --> 00:39:30,940
This is real.

819
00:39:30,940 --> 00:39:31,780
This is a real deal.

820
00:39:31,780 --> 00:39:32,820
Get out! Are you leaving?

821
00:39:33,340 --> 00:39:34,460
Or I'll shock you!

822
00:39:34,460 --> 00:39:36,166
- It's real. Careful!
- What are you doing?

823
00:39:38,300 --> 00:39:39,041
Uncle.

824
00:39:39,052 --> 00:39:40,132
- This...
- Troupe Leader.

825
00:39:40,143 --> 00:39:40,900
What happened?

826
00:39:41,060 --> 00:39:42,513
The troupe leader is here to see you.

827
00:39:42,700 --> 00:39:43,540
Troupe Leader.

828
00:39:44,020 --> 00:39:45,060
Comrade Yi Qin'e,

829
00:39:45,340 --> 00:39:46,820
I'm here representing the troupe today

830
00:39:46,820 --> 00:39:48,060
to apologize to you.

831
00:39:48,180 --> 00:39:49,820
We've criticized Pi Liang.

832
00:39:49,940 --> 00:39:50,726
He also explained

833
00:39:50,737 --> 00:39:52,060
that he drank too much last night

834
00:39:52,060 --> 00:39:53,580
and was still drunk this morning,

835
00:39:53,580 --> 00:39:55,740
so he caused trouble
in the practice room.

836
00:39:56,100 --> 00:39:57,180
But he has promised

837
00:39:57,380 --> 00:39:58,860
not to cause trouble anymore.

838
00:39:59,090 --> 00:39:59,940
Don't worry.

839
00:39:59,940 --> 00:40:01,780
Right, let's not stand here talking.

840
00:40:01,780 --> 00:40:02,620
Come on in.

841
00:40:02,820 --> 00:40:04,940
- Qin'e, invite him in.
- Please, come in.

842
00:40:04,940 --> 00:40:05,780
Okay, okay.

843
00:40:05,900 --> 00:40:06,740
Get some water.

844
00:40:07,300 --> 00:40:08,140
(Whole milk powder)

845
00:40:08,380 --> 00:40:09,460
Troupe Leader, please sit.

846
00:40:14,580 --> 00:40:16,580
It's real, and it's live. Careful.

847
00:40:22,020 --> 00:40:22,860
Troupe Leader,

848
00:40:23,020 --> 00:40:25,180
I never meant to compete for the lead.

849
00:40:26,260 --> 00:40:27,780
What's wrong with that?

850
00:40:28,180 --> 00:40:29,820
Sit, sit. Qin'e, sit down.

851
00:40:30,660 --> 00:40:33,180
Competing for roles
in the troupe is normal.

852
00:40:33,380 --> 00:40:35,820
As long as it doesn't go too far, right?

853
00:40:36,660 --> 00:40:38,340
I also spoke with Gong Lili today.

854
00:40:38,340 --> 00:40:39,560
You two just rehearse properly.

855
00:40:39,715 --> 00:40:40,929
Whoever's better gets the part.

856
00:40:40,940 --> 00:40:41,980
What's wrong with that?

857
00:40:42,620 --> 00:40:44,700
I'll just nail the fire breathing.

858
00:40:45,460 --> 00:40:46,780
The sky isn't falling.

859
00:40:47,140 --> 00:40:49,500
You need to keep going, Qin'e.

860
00:40:49,500 --> 00:40:51,460
The troupe supports you to fight for it.

861
00:40:51,740 --> 00:40:52,580
I...

862
00:40:53,060 --> 00:40:54,220
What's wrong with you?

863
00:40:54,460 --> 00:40:55,540
When Master Gu left,

864
00:40:55,540 --> 00:40:56,540
didn't he tell you that?

865
00:40:56,540 --> 00:40:59,140
He encouraged you to take the stage.

866
00:40:59,140 --> 00:41:00,060
For his sake,

867
00:41:00,180 --> 00:41:01,780
you have to see this through.

868
00:41:02,180 --> 00:41:03,180
He didn't say that.

869
00:41:04,660 --> 00:41:06,100
He just told me not to change.

870
00:41:09,100 --> 00:41:10,140
You're her uncle.

871
00:41:10,140 --> 00:41:11,180
Say something.

872
00:41:11,300 --> 00:41:12,140
Troupe Leader,

873
00:41:12,980 --> 00:41:15,060
do you still remember 1961?

874
00:41:16,860 --> 00:41:17,700
What about it?

875
00:41:18,020 --> 00:41:19,460
Shuangyang Town, Qianzhou.

876
00:41:19,713 --> 00:41:21,519
You were one of the Erjing
in Zhan Sha Chang.

877
00:41:28,380 --> 00:41:30,780
No wonder you look so familiar.

878
00:41:31,140 --> 00:41:32,220
Now, I remember.

879
00:41:32,940 --> 00:41:34,500
Back then, we owed your uncle.

880
00:41:34,700 --> 00:41:36,660
The troupe's lead drummer fainted.

881
00:41:36,660 --> 00:41:38,380
If he hadn't played onstage

882
00:41:38,380 --> 00:41:39,780
and fired up that rhythm,

883
00:41:39,940 --> 00:41:41,780
we'd have been finished up there.

884
00:41:42,980 --> 00:41:44,380
I'm truly grateful.

885
00:41:44,420 --> 00:41:46,220
Over twenty years slipped by.

886
00:41:46,220 --> 00:41:47,340
I never imagined

887
00:41:47,340 --> 00:41:48,900
we'd sit here and talk today.

888
00:41:49,340 --> 00:41:50,980
How time flies.

889
00:41:51,380 --> 00:41:52,500
So, lately, you...

890
00:41:52,540 --> 00:41:55,100
Troupe Leader, let's skip old times.

891
00:41:55,220 --> 00:41:56,540
To be honest,

892
00:41:57,180 --> 00:41:59,700
when I heard the kid was threatened,

893
00:42:00,260 --> 00:42:02,580
my first thought was:

894
00:42:02,700 --> 00:42:04,580
Forget it. We won't take this.

895
00:42:05,020 --> 00:42:06,940
She's been here for a month,

896
00:42:07,500 --> 00:42:09,380
suffering in silence.

897
00:42:10,180 --> 00:42:12,140
She says nothing, but I'm her uncle.

898
00:42:12,500 --> 00:42:14,780
Honestly, today, I just wanted

899
00:42:15,180 --> 00:42:16,380
to teach that guy a lesson.

900
00:42:16,940 --> 00:42:17,780
At worst,

901
00:42:17,940 --> 00:42:19,120
we'd just return to Ningzhou.

902
00:42:19,180 --> 00:42:20,300
No, that won't do.

903
00:42:21,020 --> 00:42:22,580
I understand how you feel.

904
00:42:22,580 --> 00:42:24,260
But you can't just go back to Ningzhou.

905
00:42:24,540 --> 00:42:25,620
No, Troupe Leader.

906
00:42:26,300 --> 00:42:27,540
Back in those days,

907
00:42:27,540 --> 00:42:29,660
when you sang on stage, starving,

908
00:42:29,740 --> 00:42:30,820
singing your heart out,

909
00:42:31,860 --> 00:42:32,820
what kept you going?

910
00:42:33,180 --> 00:42:35,460
It was your spirit, right?

911
00:42:36,180 --> 00:42:38,780
It's the same for this kid and me.

912
00:42:39,820 --> 00:42:42,580
I brought her from the Qinling Mountains

913
00:42:42,620 --> 00:42:43,740
to where we are today.

914
00:42:44,780 --> 00:42:46,660
We've never lost our spirit.

915
00:42:47,100 --> 00:42:49,860
If we give up right here today,

916
00:42:50,220 --> 00:42:52,780
all the hardships we endured

917
00:42:52,980 --> 00:42:53,860
will be for nothing.

918
00:42:54,780 --> 00:42:55,620
Alright then.

919
00:42:56,020 --> 00:42:57,140
We'll do it your way.

920
00:42:57,540 --> 00:42:58,540
Let's prove ourselves.

921
00:42:58,700 --> 00:43:00,900
Let's get this play an opera award.

922
00:43:00,900 --> 00:43:01,740
What do you say?

923
00:43:01,940 --> 00:43:03,740
Exactly. That's the spirit.

924
00:43:04,140 --> 00:43:04,980
That's right.

925
00:43:05,020 --> 00:43:06,940
=The Lead=
(Preview)

926
00:43:09,120 --> 00:43:10,360
Qin'e, you take

927
00:43:10,400 --> 00:43:11,680
these two opera excerpts.

928
00:43:11,720 --> 00:43:13,000
You took out the dramatic core.

929
00:43:13,000 --> 00:43:14,280
What's left for me to act?

930
00:43:14,440 --> 00:43:16,120
Why do you get to stand center stage?

931
00:43:16,440 --> 00:43:17,640
Get lost!

932
00:43:22,273 --> 00:43:23,600
What's going on with your troupe?

933
00:43:23,600 --> 00:43:24,680
Another violent scene?

934
00:43:24,771 --> 00:43:26,069
She didn't have feelings for him,

935
00:43:26,080 --> 00:43:27,406
but this fight might change that.

936
00:43:27,680 --> 00:43:28,680
Wasn't Laidi

937
00:43:28,800 --> 00:43:30,320
supposed to be with Feng Xiaoxiao?

938
00:43:31,080 --> 00:43:32,520
I'm here to see Comrade Yi Qing'e.

939
00:43:37,000 --> 00:43:41,620
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

940
00:43:43,090 --> 00:43:47,930
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

941
00:43:49,370 --> 00:43:53,560
♪We met and brushed past♪

942
00:43:55,120 --> 00:44:02,420
♪Your shadow drifted out of sight♪

943
00:44:16,790 --> 00:44:20,540
♪The stove fire blazed in my dream♪

944
00:44:22,140 --> 00:44:27,710
♪Lit up the tracks of pearly tears♪

945
00:44:28,830 --> 00:44:32,890
♪In my dream, water sleeves flew♪

946
00:44:34,020 --> 00:44:39,610
♪Hiding a lifetime of love♪

947
00:44:40,770 --> 00:44:44,970
♪The Qinling Mountains
crossed the stage♪

948
00:44:46,010 --> 00:44:51,640
♪Spring water brewed strong wine♪

949
00:44:52,810 --> 00:44:57,500
♪Sheep moved through the valley♪

950
00:44:58,180 --> 00:45:03,350
♪It felt like a promise
from another life♪

951
00:45:04,020 --> 00:45:09,050
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

952
00:45:10,080 --> 00:45:15,510
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

953
00:45:15,890 --> 00:45:21,170
♪If I chose again, I'd still roam♪

954
00:45:22,120 --> 00:45:27,930
♪All over this sunlit plateau♪

955
00:45:27,930 --> 00:45:33,350
♪The dream ends; the curtain falls♪

956
00:45:33,900 --> 00:45:39,410
♪Moonlight washes off this stage makeup♪

957
00:45:39,960 --> 00:45:44,920
♪The one in the mirror wears gray hair♪

958
00:45:45,940 --> 00:45:51,220
♪Already sang all my joy and sorrow♪

959
00:45:52,020 --> 00:46:01,050
♪Already shouted across Qinchuan Plain♪
